<br>
Im not a MCH yet (I am at 3-4-2-4), so i am currently using pets like graul maulers, Ravenous Tortons, a 2 Boar Wolf Combo, etc...<br>
<br>
My problem is this ..<br>
<br>
Every time i send one of my pets after imps, it is bled, set on fire and incapacitated within 10 seconds of the word "Attack".<br>
<br>
The main reason for this is Fire. Is there any defence against this? Are there any pets that dont catch on fire and fall in 10 seconds? Is it special "Heat" protection that will prevent fire damage? And furthermore, is there any defence for ME against this? I wear a bit of composite/padded armor (not a lot of it -- 4 pieces), but it makes no difference.<br>
<br>
Is there a "Stop, drop and Roll" command? Cause i have not found a way to put the fire out, other than waiting about 3-4 minutes until my health is so wounded tht it takes 15 min in a med centre to recover.<br>
<br>
First aid doesnt seem to do anything ... can Doctors put out fire?<br>
<br>
If anyone has any pet suggestions (better pets to use) or an idea of how to put out fire/prevent it from hitting me, please help :)<br>
<br>
Just trying to last more than 10 seconds in PVP ... <br>
