<br>
Thx for tips on pets ... I was kinda hoping there was a pet out there that just laughed at fire damage and ran right through it ;)<br>
<br>
The main difficulty i had was, i was being sniped and set on fire ... i had thought that Flamethrower had a really short range, but the people hitting me were 64 meters + on top of a hill shooting down (The hills behind the shuttleport in Anchorhead). So i would send my pet and he wouldnt even get up the hill before being mowed down. I am talking literally 5-8 seconds of life before being incapacitated.<br>
<br>
And i was out of pistol range when being set on fire .. or just barely in pistol range ... cant remember which, but i DO remember that i never even got close enough to fire off more than 2 shots.<br>
<br>
Are there any other weapons besides Flamethrower that have the ability to set someone on fire? Or is it just the Flamethrower has a much better range than i thought?<br>
<br>
cheers! <p>Bards - the &quot;clothing-optional&quot; class.<br>
