<br>
Still wish there was a "stop, drop and roll" command tho :)<br>
<br>
In the future, i guess it IS just a matter of patience and guile when dealing with a commando team who start sniping from the vantage point of the hill above the Anchorhead shuttleport...<br>
<br>
Ill remember about the storing of pets, and the "run towards water" thing. On tatooine, you are right .. not really an option, but hey :)<br>
